name: MegaDildoV01
description:
PLEASE NOTE: This is my first model I have ever created. I used the Merge Block Weighted extension for AUTOMATIC1111 to bring together Dreamlike PhotoReal 2.0 and LarryAIDraw/baka_gape_nainsfw_10. After a great deal of trial and error I settled on using the SMOOTHSTEP^2 preset.

This model focuses specifically on huge dildo insertions. It was intended for all kinds of insertions and gaping but so far it works best on dildos.

The model responds reasonably well to Danbooru tags, and responds very well to the tags listed.

You can get other poses if you work the prompt hard enough, but the phrase "squatting on a huge dildo" will get immediate results.

The use of vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned.vae.pt and the negative models bad_prompt_version2, and bad-hands-5, are highly recommended.

The model combines well with most textual embeddings.

Recommended settings

Sampling Steps: 20-25

Sampling method: Euler a

Restore faces: on

Highres fix: on

CFG Scale: 7 for txt2img and 15 for img2img

Dreamlike PhotoReal uses a modified CreativeML OpenRAIL-M license. Please be sure to read and comply with it.
